description:
The phenomenal freelancer, solo but not alone is a glimpse into the world of freelancing through the eye's & experience of someone's who's been in the trenches, has conquered doubt, and is using the web to create an empire. I'm a fiverr Top Rated Seller, the inventor of a safer way to stash with Quirky + GE, and an internet entrepreneur-ing, web adventuring freelance graphic + web designer who's fruitfully freelanced for the greater part of a decade.. I will show exactly what I believe is the very best way to live a freelance lifestyle.

I'm Dion Lynk your instructor for this course that is truly near and dear to my heart. I've been using the internet as a means to build my ideas for close to 10 years now, and I must say that its been an awesome ride! In this course I'll teach you about; the money, your health as a freelancer, productivity tools, time management tips and so much more!
title: The Phenomenal Freelancer
